msgid "Scenario VII: Return to The Depths of Yoth"
msgstr "冒险VII：重返幽嘶深渊"

msgid "Search the collection for the new Harbinger of Valusia <i>(The Sleeper Returns)</i> and place damage on it equal to the amount of damage recorded in parentheses in your Campaign Log. Because it is agenda 5a or 6a, place it in the pursuit area. (See “Pursuit,” below.)"
msgstr "搜索收藏找出瓦卢西亚的预示者<i>(沉睡者归来)</i>，并按照冒险日志括号内记录的伤害总数，在瓦卢西亚的预示者上放置对应数量的伤害。因为从密谋5a或6a开始游戏，将放在一边的瓦卢西亚的预示者敌人放到追击区域。(见下文，“追击”。)"

msgid "Search the collection for the new Harbinger of Valusia <i>(The Sleeper Returns)</i> and set it aside, out of play. Place damage on it equal to the amount of damage recorded in parentheses in your Campaign Log. If the Harbinger of Valusia would enter play during this scenario, use this version instead of the original one."
msgstr "搜索收藏，找出新版的瓦卢西亚的预示者<i>(沉睡者归来)</i>并将其放在一边，位于场外。按照冒险日志括号内记录的伤害总数，在瓦卢西亚的预示者上放置对应数量的伤害。如果在本冒险期间，瓦卢西亚的预示者将要入场，不使用原版，改为使用其新版。"

msgid "Shuffle the Perils of Yoth treachery into the exploration deck."
msgstr "将幽嘶险境诡计卡混洗入探索牌堆。"

msgid "<b>Forced</b> - After a new exploration deck is created during act 1b: Search the encounter deck, discard pile, and all out-of-play areas for Perils of Yoth and shuffle it into the exploration deck. Shuffle the encounter deck if it was searched."
msgstr "<b>强制</b> - 在场景1b期间创建新的探索牌堆后：查找遭遇牌堆、弃牌堆和所有场外区域，找出幽嘶险境并将其混洗入探索牌堆。如果查找过遭遇牌堆则将其混洗。"

msgid "Do you remember that you “collected a strange liquid”?"
msgstr "你是否曾“收集了一种奇怪的液体”？"

msgid "Check your supplies. If any investigator has sticky goop:"
msgstr "查看你的补给品。如果任意调查员有黏液团："

msgid "The liquid from the fountain dissolves the viscous substance, revealing a solid object beneath the ooze. Record \"Key of Eztli\" in any one investigator's supplies."
msgstr "泉中的液体溶解了黏性物质，黏液下露出了一个坚实物体。在任意调查员的补给品中记录“埃兹特里之钥”。"

msgid "Key of Eztli"
msgstr "埃兹特里之钥"

msgid "The Key of Eztli."
msgstr "埃兹特里之钥。"
